Package msp.simulator.dynamic

Class Dynamic

  • java.lang.Object
    • msp.simulator.dynamic.Dynamic

  • public class Dynamic
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the top class to handle all of the dynamic processing in the simulation. It includes all of the interactions, linear or rotational, between the environment and the satellite.
    Author:
    Florian CHAUBEYRE
